一名中間人在7月17日向周提出給予相等於500萬的雙倍競選經費及政府官職勸退立法會選舉，使選票集中於何君堯<ref name="emag1">{{cite web|url=https://eweekly.hk/article/_title/042_Book_A_Cover_pos5jgoamcf|title=中間人出價500萬 勸新西候選人周永勤退選|date=2016-08-18|publisher=[[E週刊|E週刊]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828031814/https://eweekly.hk/article/_title/042_Book_A_Cover_pos5jgoamcf|archivedate=2016-08-28|accessdate=2016-08-27}}</ref><ref name="lc16ab-sn1">{{cite web|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A3%84%E9%81%B8%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E8%A5%BF-%E7%A8%B1-%E5%94%94%E6%83%B3%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9-%E6%9B%BE%E5%82%B3%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%8B%B8%E9%80%80%E8%AE%93%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF/|title=自由黨周永勤棄選新界西 稱為免身邊人惹麻煩 曾傳出中間人勸退讓路何君堯|date=2016-08-25|publisher=[[立場新聞|立場新聞]]|access-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918222645/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A3%84%E9%81%B8%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E8%A5%BF-%E7%A8%B1-%E5%94%94%E6%83%B3%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E7%85%A9-%E6%9B%BE%E5%82%B3%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%8B%B8%E9%80%80%E8%AE%93%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF/|archive-date=2016-09-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="air-con">{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20160831/2_422988_0/%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E7%A6%81%E5%8D%80%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-500%E8%90%AC%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%98%E5%8A%A0%E5%AE%98%E8%81%B7-%E5%86%8D%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E8%BA%AB%E9%82%8A%E4%BA%BA|title=周永勤機場禁區爆料》獨家有片！500萬利誘加官職 再恐嚇威脅身邊人|date=2016-08-31|publisher=[[壹週刊_(香港)|壹週刊]]|access-date=2016-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903152456/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20160831/2_422988_0/%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E7%A6%81%E5%8D%80%E7%88%86%E6%96%99-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-500%E8%90%AC%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%98%E5%8A%A0%E5%AE%98%E8%81%B7-%E5%86%8D%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E8%BA%AB%E9%82%8A%E4%BA%BA|archive-date=2016-09-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。周在[[都市日報|都市日報]]旗下《[[E週刊|E週刊]]》於8月18日的報導上承認事件<ref name="emag1"/><ref name="lc16ab-sn1"/>，並於8月21日在[[Facebook|Facebook]]發出「不要[[中央人民政府駐香港特別行政區聯絡辦公室|西環]]治新西」的圖像回應<ref name="lc16ab-sn1"/>。

在8月25日上午，周收到兩段恐嚇錄音，並在下午轉交傳媒<ref name="lc16ab-sn2">{{cite web|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A3%84%E9%81%B8-%E7%94%B7%E8%81%B2%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3-%E5%8F%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%A2%E9%96%8B%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87%E7%84%A1%E5%BF%83%E6%A9%9F/|title=【周永勤棄選】男聲狙擊錄音曝光：召集二三十人狙擊 等佢開論壇無心機|date=2016-08-26|publisher=[[立場新聞|立場新聞]]|access-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001231/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A3%84%E9%81%B8-%E7%94%B7%E8%81%B2%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3-%E5%8F%AC%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%89%E5%8D%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%A2%E9%96%8B%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87%E7%84%A1%E5%BF%83%E6%A9%9F/|archive-date=2017-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。結果他選擇在晚上由[[香港有線電視|香港有線電視]]舉辦的選舉論壇上穿黑衣出席、沒有安排團隊撐場及不佈置任何橫額及直幡<ref name="lc16ab-sn1"/><ref name="lc16ab-mp1">{{cite web|url=http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160825/s00001/1472130929522|title=【短片：周永勤棄選】遭鄭松泰質問「獨自微笑」 何君堯稱保持樂觀：香港人需要振作！|date=2016-08-25|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|access-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826201931/http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160825/s00001/1472130929522|archive-date=2016-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。周在開場發言隨即表示因受到威嚇，不想身邊的人惹上更高層次的麻煩，宣布停止一切選舉活動<ref name="le16ab-ad1">{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160825/55554866|title=【立會選戰】自由黨周永勤突退選：死唔可怕 最可怕是保護不到身邊人|date=2016-08-25|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]|access-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826191753/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160825/55554866|archive-date=2016-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，等同退選{{efn|因為立法會條例規定「候選人只可在提名期結束前退出競選」，故周即使自行放棄參選，仍然是選票上的候選人<ref name="le16ab-ad1"/><ref name="le16ab-mp2"/>。}}，並向鏡頭鞠躬致歉<ref name="le16ab-ad1"/>。論壇中[[鄭松泰|鄭松泰]]質問何君堯為何在周就退選發言時獨自暗笑，何指自己遇上逆境都會保持樂觀，斥責鄭指控形同抹黑<ref name="lc16ab-mp1"/>。在論壇完結時，周引用[[村上春樹|村上春樹]]的[[雞蛋與高牆|雞蛋與高牆]]演說，指自己不怕當雞蛋挑戰高牆，重申因考慮身邊人會惹上麻煩及負上代價，決定退選<ref name="le16ab-ad1"/>。周在離開電視台時被記者問及家人情況，他嚎哭並稱自己不想說<ref name="icac-s1">{{cite web|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B7%A5%E9%BB%A8%E6%8E%A5%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E7%AB%8B%E6%A1%88%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A3%84%E9%81%B8/|title=工黨接通知 廉署立案調查周永勤棄選|publisher=[[立場新聞|立場新聞]]|date=2016-08-29|access-date=2016-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305001058/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B7%A5%E9%BB%A8%E6%8E%A5%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E7%AB%8B%E6%A1%88%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E6%A3%84%E9%81%B8/|archive-date=2017-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

何君堯在論壇結束後表示周退選一事與自己無關，而周早前對他原居民身分的質疑已向選管會作出投訴，無迫周退選的動機<ref name="hwyre852"/>，更形容為周「處心積慮，自導自演」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://topick.hket.com/article/1490980/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E8%99%95%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8D%E6%85%AE%20%E8%87%AA%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%AA%E6%BC%94|title=何君堯：周永勤處心積慮 自導自演|date=2016-08-26|publisher=[[香港經濟日報|香港經濟日報]]|access-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827203107/http://topick.hket.com/article/1490980/%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%EF%BC%9A%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E8%99%95%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8D%E6%85%AE%20%E8%87%AA%E5%B0%8E%E8%87%AA%E6%BC%94|archive-date=2016-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然如此，何在8月26日於[[香港商業電台|香港商業電台]]節目中承認錄音中的男聲是其團隊的義工，但就指是內部已放棄計劃的錄音，認為周涉嫌[[竊聽|竊聽]]<ref name="lc16ab-sn2"/><ref name="le16ab-mp2">{{cite web|url=http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160826/s00001/1472174057857|title=【周永勤棄選】何君堯指錄音為內部策略討論 反質疑周從何獲得 強調論壇前已決定不狙擊|date=2016-08-26|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|access-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827190823/http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160826/s00001/1472174057857|archive-date=2016-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，何的義工黃四川承認是自己錄音，但就稱完全沒威脅周，更指如周面對不了壓力不應出席論壇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160826/s00001/1472195988952|title=【訪問錄音：周永勤棄選】追擊聲帶主角黃四川：百分百沒有威脅對方|date=2016-08-26|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|access-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827200417/http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20160826/s00001/1472195988952|archive-date=2016-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

然而，自由黨對周退選一事並不知情，[[田北俊|田北俊]]及[[鍾國斌|鍾國斌]]等黨員均是在觀看選舉論壇或被記者查詢才知道周的決定<ref name="lc16ab-sn1"/><ref name="lc16ab-mp1"/>，但及後田則承認[[中央人民政府駐香港特別行政區聯絡辦公室|香港中聯辦]]早在7月已為確保何的選情而要求他勸退周<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BF%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A67%E6%9C%88%E6%89%BE%E6%88%91%E5%8B%B8%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E5%8B%BF%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-%E5%85%8D%E7%A4%99%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%B8%E6%83%85/|title=田北俊：中聯辦7月找我　勸周永勤勿參選　免礙何君堯選情|date=2016-09-14|publisher=[[立場新聞|立場新聞]]|access-date=2016-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001182112/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BF%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A67%E6%9C%88%E6%89%BE%E6%88%91%E5%8B%B8%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E5%8B%BF%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-%E5%85%8D%E7%A4%99%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E9%81%B8%E6%83%85/|archive-date=2018-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而周梁淑怡及[[劉健儀|劉健儀]]在8月26日下午則到[[廉政公署總部大樓|廉政公署總部大樓]]報案，要求徹查<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1281521-20160826.htm?share=twitter|title=周梁淑怡及劉健儀就周永勤事件到廉署報案|date=2016-08-26|publisher=[[香港電台|香港電台]]|access-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914015725/http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1281521-20160826.htm?share=twitter|archive-date=2016-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[廉政公署_(香港)|廉政公署]]在接報後於8月29日向所有報案人士通知已開始立案調查事件<ref name="icac-s1"/>。

周在8月26日深夜乘搭航班至[[英國|英國]]，他在[[香港國際機場|香港國際機場]]表示施壓者勢力比中聯辨或[[黑社會|黑社會]]更強大，超出[[紀律部隊|紀律部隊]]的執法範圍，故沒有報案<ref name="air-con"/>。他更擔心被人[[綁票|綁票]]而不敢到[[中國大陸|中國大陸]]、[[泰國|泰國]]及[[緬甸|緬甸]]<ref name="air-con"/>，亦因英國閉路電視較多容易偵查罪行<ref name="after16le-ap">{{cite web|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20160905/2_425209_0/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%BE%8C%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E8%A6%AA%E4%BA%BA-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%BD%B1%E6%88%91%E7%9B%B8|title=《選舉後周永勤秘密回港》機場獨家有片：強勢力恐嚇親人 英國都有人影我相|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]|date=2016-09-05|access-date=2016-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160908085309/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20160905/2_425209_0/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%BE%8C%E5%91%A8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8B%A4%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E6%81%90%E5%9A%87%E8%A6%AA%E4%BA%BA-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%BD%B1%E6%88%91%E7%9B%B8|archive-date=2016-09-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而選擇去英國探望朋友並在選舉結束後回港<ref name="air-con"/>。周亦道出自己為香港現時的政治環境而傷心，認為是次可能是香港最後一個有選擇的選舉<ref name="air-con"/>。

